Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:34.23,Tsuritama_Flashback,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura-chan isn't with you, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.23,0:01:35.72,Tsuritama_Flashback,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,We can't find her anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.72,0:01:37.82,Tsuritama_Flashback,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura-chan's missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:41.74,Ep_Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,520)}Joyous Fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:41.06,Tsuritama_Italics/Thought,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,It was the beginning of a long night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:44.16,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura! Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:45.01,Tsuritama_Main,TAMOTSU,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.01,0:01:46.32,Tsuritama_Main,MARIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.32,0:01:47.68,Tsuritama_Main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.68,0:01:49.12,Tsuritama_Main,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.12,0:01:51.26,Tsuritama_Main,HEIHACHI,0000,0000,0000,,She's been spirited away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:53.47,Tsuritama_Main,ERIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, there's no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.47,0:01:57.74,Tsuritama_Main,HEIHACHI,0000,0000,0000,,Erika, what's illustrated \Nhere isn't fantasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.74,0:02:02.02,Tsuritama_Main,HEIHACHI,0000,0000,0000,,It's even said his first victim \Nwill be a young child.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.02,0:02:05.38,Tsuritama_Main,FISHERMAN,0000,0000,0000,,I heard she was heading \Ntowards the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:09.90,Tsuritama_Main,HEIHACHI,0000,0000,0000,,This is the work of the dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.18,0:02:12.86,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Ten-year-old Usami Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:16.02,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Approximately 144\Ncentimeters tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:17.95,Tsuritama_Main,MINION A,0000,0000,0000,,What is her connection to JF1?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:20.13,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I do not know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.13,0:02:23.12,Tsuritama_Main,MINION B,0000,0000,0000,,We do not know JF1's \Ncurrent location either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:25.70,Tsuritama_Main,MINION C,0000,0000,0000,,It will be too late if we \Nwait for something to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:28.36,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We should secure JF1.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:32.40,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Find the girl first. Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:51.10,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Tapioca, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.49,0:02:53.77,Tsuritama_Flashback,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:57.82,Tsuritama_Flashback,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:02:59.78,Tsuritama_Flashback,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.87,0:03:02.49,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:06.05,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go? Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:08.18,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-chan, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:10.89,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Nii-chan. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:12.63,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.63,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:19.65,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:23.09,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:24.88,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:26.43,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.86,0:03:30.93,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for what I said earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:35.28,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,But, I really do think \NSakura-chan was sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:37.08,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I think she might have been
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:39.11,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,overwhelmed by all her pent-up\Nfeelings and sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:41.53,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying Sakura \Nchose to disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:44.83,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:47.30,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura would never do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:47.87,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.61,0:03:50.50,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:53.91,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about \Nparents or siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:57.84,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,My parents are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:01.35,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think they'll ever come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:05.22,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure families have \Na lot to deal with,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:07.76,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm jealous of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:11.80,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I've never laughed or \Nfought with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:17.32,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I don't understand, \Nbut I'm worried, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:18.94,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act like you're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:25.76,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:27.57,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.30,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:37.81,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:42.80,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,When searching for someone,\Nyou must put yourself in their shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:46.81,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing more than \Nmy personal opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:51.02,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I believe she went to see her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:54.55,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:57.73,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Think. Only you know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:24.97,Tsuritama_Main,SAKURA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about Onii-chan \Nany more. It's his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:28.42,Tsuritama_Main,SAKURA,0000,0000,0000,,I won't apologize to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:40.44,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:41.62,Tsuritama_Main,SAKURA,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:47.64,Tsuritama_Main,SAKURA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:48.91,Tsuritama_Main,SAKURA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:51.40,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where you've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:54.71,Tsuritama_Main,SAKURA,0000,0000,0000,,We came here with Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:58.79,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebait ice cream. We had that here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.95,0:06:03.47,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You must have been lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:06.49,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:21.10,Tsuritama_Main,SAKURA,0000,0000,0000,,Mari-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:22.10,Tsuritama_Main,MARIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.74,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:34.16,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:37.50,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:42.07,Tsuritama_Main,SAKURA,0000,0000,0000,,Mari-chan, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:42.98,Tsuritama_Main,MARIKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:46.61,Tsuritama_Main,TAMOTSU,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Sakura. I'm sorry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:49.38,Tsuritama_Main,MIRKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad. I'm so glad you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:54.70,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,La la la, dum ta-dum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:58.34,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good, good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:06:59.48,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,La la la, dum ta-dum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:06:59.48,Tsuritama_Overlap,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:04.43,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you tell me the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:07.89,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you already know,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:10.57,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I am a member of the \Nalien investigation and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:14.52,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,apprehension organization, Duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:22.86,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come to Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:24.84,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,We came to catch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.05,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.43,0:07:28.97,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean the beast \Nunder that bait ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:32.06,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's one of our kind who came
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:33.78,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,to Earth a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:36.47,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,He's been traveling \NEarth's oceans doing naughty
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:38.27,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,things like moving ships around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:43.08,Tsuritama_Italics/Thought,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Alien life forms really are \Nresponsible for Bermuda Syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.47,0:07:46.84,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know what he'll \Ndo if we leave him be,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:48.23,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,so we came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:51.15,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,We came here to catch him \Nand take him back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.69,0:07:53.95,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,How did you plan to catch him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:57.86,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to subdue him is \Nto get him out of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:08:00.84,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Communicating using water's \Nnormal for our kind,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:02.67,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but for some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:05.04,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,when we try to use water \Nto talk to people,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:08.09,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,we end up controlling them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:10.97,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,We don't get along well \Nwith humans at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:13.85,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,And he forgets his own strength a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:15.52,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,so he's really dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:18.99,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you intended to \Nfish him out of the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:22.28,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I was going to \Ncatch him with Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:24.14,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you try to \Ncatch him yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:26.30,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,We've never fished before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:29.09,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if we're not careful, \Nwe'll be affected by him
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:31.01,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and go crazy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:33.87,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,We were going to have Yuki catch him
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:36.06,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,while we suppressed his powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:37.62,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,He was strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:41.12,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,He took total control over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:43.17,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,He really is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:48.21,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even sure if the two \Nof us together can stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:52.13,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's not too bad now,\Nbut if he gets even stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:53.35,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:55.22,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,His voice might even reach
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:58.18,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,people through the moisture in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.25,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,What if the humidity were \Nto suddenly increase,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:02.04,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,such as when it rains or storms?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:04.06,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:07.04,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,If the air's filled with water,\Neveryone on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:10.61,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,will fall under his spell \Nand dance the Enoshima Dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:13.53,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking about it makes me hurt here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:16.48,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to your planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:18.57,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let Duck handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:21.89,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Catching him won't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:25.41,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless, you tried to involve humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:27.11,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I know that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:29.94,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot allow you to \Ncontinue what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:42.94,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,What's a whitebait cafe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:45.16,Tsuritama_Main,TAMOTSU,0000,0000,0000,,It's a whitebait cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:46.17,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:47.98,Tsuritama_Main,TAMOTSU,0000,0000,0000,,I'm renovating the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:50.81,Tsuritama_Main,TAMOTSU,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of whitebait and Enoshima bowls,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:52.00,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna sell all kinds of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:53.91,Tsuritama_Main,TAMOTSU,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebait bowls, whitebait pizza,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:55.98,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,whitebait ice cream, whitebait steamed buns.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:57.24,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're overextending yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:10:00.26,Tsuritama_Main,TAMOTSU,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be sure until you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:01.63,Tsuritama_Main,TAMOTSU,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:03.54,Tsuritama_Main,TAMOTSU,0000,0000,0000,,If you think of something, try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:05.04,Tsuritama_Main,TAMOTSU,0000,0000,0000,,You won't know until you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.51,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:08.12,Tsuritama_Main,TAMOTSU,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:11.94,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.15,Tsuritama_Main,TAMOTSU,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:14.71,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:17.09,Tsuritama_Main,TAMOTSU,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll be happier that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:20.98,Tsuritama_Main,TAMOTSU,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're serious about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:22.77,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:24.74,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:29.98,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,When he's by himself, he's thinking \Nabout something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:32.64,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Nii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:56.24,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you take a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:56.95,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:01.45,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad Sakura-chan is all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:02.39,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:12.30,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:13.28,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:17.66,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy we found Sakura-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:18.73,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:22.27,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki's going to have a new mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:25.39,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really happy for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:26.58,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:30.37,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.26,0:11:33.78,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about families,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:38.33,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't know about \Nparents or how he feels,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:40.98,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I just wanted to \Ntell Natsuki something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.53,0:11:42.98,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:47.06,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I said I was jealous of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:49.14,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:52.52,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been messed up inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:56.75,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I realized I must have been \Nlonely for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:59.46,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,But I could never say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.78,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, saying it wouldn't have helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:06.56,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I thought saying something would've\Nscrewed everything up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:11.56,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,But I... Grandma, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:12.83,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:16.70,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I've got people I can \Ntalk to about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:19.91,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,When I realized I could tell him anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:22.80,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:23.80,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:27.86,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I was lonely, but that was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:30.27,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go back,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.89,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm not embarrassed \Nabout what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.40,0:12:34.83,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I had you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.47,0:12:41.15,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I've been fine with having\Nyou as my dad and mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:44.42,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:47.60,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:49.74,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:53.53,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:56.17,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:04.65,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Koko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:05.47,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.69,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Koko, do you like Enoshima?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.60,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:12.75,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,The whitebait's good, \Nand everyone's so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:14.35,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:16.35,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,I like it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.94,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:20.58,Tsuritama_Main,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-chan, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:23.28,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided. I've decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.81,0:13:26.70,Tsuritama_Italics/Thought,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-chan, you're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:29.30,Tsuritama_Italics/Thought,KOKO,0000,0000,0000,,You really are an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:38.41,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:56.46,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:57.67,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:13:59.84,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,Is your sadness all better?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:00.69,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:01.82,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:04.26,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Keito, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:06.45,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:08.84,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Eat lots and rest lots.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:10.00,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:11.78,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Don't carry anything heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:12.79,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:15.89,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:17.63,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:18.58,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:21.75,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say when you leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:24.84,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:28.97,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Be sure you \Nsay it when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:29.89,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:33.50,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave without saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:34.51,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:37.43,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, I'll be mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:39.73,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:42.99,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,Be nice to everyone until you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.99,0:14:44.40,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:46.79,Tsuritama_Main,KEITO,0000,0000,0000,,Smile and hold your head high.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:49.28,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Smile and hold your head high.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:17.73,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:23.48,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't settled our match yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:25.45,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,We'll let size decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:27.55,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who catches the smallest one...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:29.49,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Another punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:32.03,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:34.43,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wouldn't fish any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:36.16,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,I will. I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:37.81,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, bring it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:42.29,Tsuritama_Main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Eno... shima... Bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:51.08,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could stay like this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:53.72,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kidding, I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:56.59,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Forget what I said! How embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.19,0:15:58.24,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:00.83,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could stay like this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:05.84,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the world ends tomorrow, \NI know I'll be fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.93,0:16:11.82,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,The world won't end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:16.20,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be sad if it ended. \NI love Enoshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:25.29,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,I had fun. Everything was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:28.38,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like you're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:29.42,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:32.22,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! What are you talking about, Haru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:33.96,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:39.12,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:40.15,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.32,0:16:43.02,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Haru, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:47.82,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Raise your rod, \Nand... What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:49.09,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:53.02,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, it's okay. I can do it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:58.45,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Akira, 62 centimeters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:01.03,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Haru, 56 centimeters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.03,0:17:02.79,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:07.12,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki... 78? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:08.75,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, you're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:09.96,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Natsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:11.70,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:14.36,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:16.97,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,43!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:20.57,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki, punishment! Bi bi bi bi biii!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:22.94,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll let you guys off easy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:24.28,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You're bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:27.59,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I'm going to catch a bass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:30.86,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,A black bass. A really huge one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:32.88,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,You're aiming to be a professional?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.61,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a lot of work?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:37.36,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,You won't know until you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:39.45,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I know you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:41.83,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:46.68,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Akira, Natsuki's punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.68,0:17:48.19,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:49.84,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:53.32,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,There's something that's \Nbeen bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:54.39,Tsuritama_Main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:56.84,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki, don't you think \Nyour hair's too long?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:58.68,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:02.10,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you smiling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:05.11,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,I've got scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:08.80,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:11.89,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.89,0:18:13.78,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:15.37,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:17.11,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:26.29,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Those bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:27.75,Tsuritama_Main,SAKURA,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:30.55,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry. I woke you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:31.75,Tsuritama_Main,SAKURA,0000,0000,0000,,Your hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:33.91,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,They went and cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:35.70,Tsuritama_Main,SAKURA,0000,0000,0000,,So? It looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:39.14,Tsuritama_Main,SAKURA,0000,0000,0000,,You're terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:42.19,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I've never done this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:45.05,Tsuritama_Main,SAKURA,0000,0000,0000,,Watch. It's like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:48.25,Tsuritama_Main,SAKURA,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:52.55,Tsuritama_Main,SAKURA,0000,0000,0000,,I love Mari-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:54.38,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:57.95,Tsuritama_Main,SAKURa,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes I want to talk about Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:19:02.20,Tsuritama_Main,NATSUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's do that when \Nit's just you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:07.87,Tsuritama_Main,SAKURA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Hey, do you remember \Nthat time on Mom's birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:11.01,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Tapioca, I've made my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:13.79,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the opinion of an individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:17.80,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,It is the objective opinion \Nof a Duck investigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:20.97,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Tapioca.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:27.08,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:29.73,Tsuritama_Main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:31.83,Tsuritama_Main,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:34.32,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been acting weird today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:38.60,Tsuritama_Italics/Thought,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I know now
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:44.04,Tsuritama_Italics/Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,what Haru tried to say to me then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:48.28,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,This is Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:51.62,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have important\Ninformation regarding JF1.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:56.32,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,JF1 is not a dangerous alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:20:00.97,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,He holds the key to explaining \NBermuda Syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:03.72,Tsuritama_Main,BOSS,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.11,0:20:07.31,Tsuritama_Main,BOSS,0000,0000,0000,,We have sent a combat unit to Enoshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:09.30,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,A combat unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:15.11,Tsuritama_Main,BOSS,0000,0000,0000,,We have determined the unusual \Nevents occurring in the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:17.69,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,vicinity of Enoshima to be the \Nproduct of Bermuda Syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:22.28,Tsuritama_Main,BOSS,0000,0000,0000,,Our mission is to attack \Nand remove aliens
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:25.03,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,who pose a threat to humankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:31.96,Tsuritama_Main,BOSS,0000,0000,0000,,JF1 is one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:37.88,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait! Haru is... \NJF1 is not dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:39.70,Tsuritama_Main,AKIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I have confirmed this with my own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:42.38,Tsuritama_Main,BOSS,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really Yamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.86,0:20:46.14,Tsuritama_Main,BOSS,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really a proud \Ninvestigator of Duck?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:52.68,Tsuritama_Italics/Thought,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Haru was telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:56.80,Tsuritama_Main,TV,0000,0000,0000,,The typhoon which appeared \Nin the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:21:01.32,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,west of the Mariana Islands,\Nis slowly growing and
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:03.42,Tsuritama_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,moving north towards Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:07.47,Tsuritama_Italics/Thought,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Danger was at Earth's doorstep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:15.31,Tsuritama_Italics/Thought,YUKI,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't have much time left.
